# language: en

Feature: Shopping Cart

  Scenario: View shopping cart

    Given I am on the products page
    When I have a product added to the shopping cart
    And I click on "Cart" in the top right corner
    Then I should see the products I added to the cart

  Scenario: Remove product from shopping cart

    Given I am on the cart page
    When I have a product added to the shopping cart
    And I click on "Remove"
    Then the product should be removed from the shopping cart

  Scenario: Proceed to checkout

    Given I am on the cart page
    When I have a product added to the shopping cart
    And I click on "Checkout"
    Then I should be redirected to the "Your Information" page
